            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=2013-super-favorites">2013-super-favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=coming-of-age">coming-of-age</a>, 
